{"word":"ἐκπετάννυμι","slug":"ἐκπετάννυμι","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἐκπετάννυμι</b></el> <el>(<a href='S:future tense'>fut.</a> <el>-πετάσω</el>) (aor1 <a href='S:passive signification'><a href='S:Passive Voice'>pass.</a></a> <el>ἐξεπετάσθην</el>) (<a href='S:perfect tense'>perf.</a> <el>ἐκπεπέτασμαι</el>) </el><p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><i>to spread out</i>, of a sail, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b>; of wings, <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b>; of a net, Orac. <a href='S:apud (quoted in)'>ap.</a> <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b><a href='S:metaphorically'>metaph.</a>, <el>ἐπὶ κῶμον ἐκπετασθείς</el> <i>wholly given up to</i> revel, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}